### Football Betting API - Matches Tests
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### 1. All Matches
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches

### 2. Today's Matches (Short Route)
GET {{baseUrl}}/today

### 4.  Live Matches (Full Route)
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches/live

GET {{baseUrl}}/matches/leagues/all

### 6.  Matches with Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?status=SCHEDULED&limit=10&offset=0

### 7. Get Matches by League
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?league=Premier League

### 8. Get Matches by Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?dateFrom=2024-01-01&dateTo=2024-12-31

### 9. Get Premier League Matches
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches/competition/PL

### 10. Get La Liga Matches
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches/competition/PD

### 11. Get Bundesliga Matches
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches/competition/BL1

### 12. Get Serie A Matches
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches/competition/SA

### 13. Get Champions League Matches
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches/competition/CL

### 14. Get Match by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches/1

### 15. Get Today's Matches (Public Route)
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/matches/today

### 16. Get This Week's Matches
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/matches/week

### 17. Get Popular League Matches
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/matches/popular

### 18. Get Match Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/matches/stats

### 19. Trigger Manual Fixture Sync (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/matches/sync

### 20. Get Matches with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?limit=5&offset=10

### 21. Get Finished Matches
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?status=FINISHED

### 22. Get In-Play Matches
GET {{baseUrl}}/matches?status=IN_PLAY
